This template will superimpose [[United States military award devices]] onto [[Awards and decorations of the United States military|military award ribbons]].  It currently does [[oak leaf cluster]]s, [[award star]]s, [[service star]]s (up to a numeric value of 24 total awards) as well as the [[Arrowhead device]], [[Valor device|Combat V]], and [[Fleet Marine Force Combat Operations Insignia]].  Variables are as follows:

